Release Manager Doc
===================

This document is a checklist of all the actiities to be
done for a release.

* Update all the site docs: src/site
* pom.xml -> change version number
* Verify backword compatibility: ./testBackwardCompatibility.sh
* Change version number in: src/main/shell/wizcrypt
* Change version number in RPM spec file: wizcrypt.spec
* Create a tag with the version number
* Upload the artifacts to release site
* Update site with: target/site
* Update http://freshmeat.net/
* Blog, digg, etc!

